//(Financial application: compute future tuition) Suppose that the tuition for a university is $10,000 this year and increases 5% every year. In one year, the tuition
//will be $10,500. Write a program that computes the tuition in ten years and the
//total cost of four yearsâ€™ worth of tuition after the tenth year.
public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int x=10000;
        for(int i=1;i<=10;i++)
            x=x+x*5/100;
        System.out.println("tuition after ten years is: "+x);
        int sum=x;
        for(int i=1;i<=3;i++)
        {x=x+x*5/100;
        sum=sum+x;}
        System.out.println("tuition of 4 years is : "+sum);
    }
}
